      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Dhanwantry, Kalyan R &lt;kalyan.r.dhanwantry@intel.com&gt;,Sherman, Wendy S &lt;wendy.s.sherman@intel.com&gt;, Kasturi, Sri Harisha Sai &lt;sri.harisha.sai.kasturi@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7C32437E-C196-40F9-ABE4-6AAB603008E2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Inventory Report, Min Max/ROP data will be shared with DSV accordingly to that they can calculate ROP and Min Max data need to update in SAP</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C8010638-0F62-4328-9037-FFECBF747289" signavio:alignment="left">
